A middle-aged man's face gradually transforming through four seamless stages from left to right, showing the progression of growing a full beard - starting clean-shaven, then stubble, then short beard, finally a thick distinguished beard. Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, warm golden afternoon lighting, gentle wind slightly tousling the hair, expressive thoughtful eyes that remain constant through the transformation, subtle cherry blossom petals floating in the background, the figure wearing a simple comfortable sweater, conveying a sense of personal evolution and the quiet passage of time.
